px" face="verdana" color="#ffffff">For more information please contact our support team at </font><a href=''${siteURL}''><font  style="font-size:11px; line-height:16px" face="verdana" color="#ffffff">${supportEmail}</font></a><br>\r\n    </td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n</body>'
